subNodes.name: function()externalpayable{if(balances[owner]>=reserveCap){EtherInWei=EtherInWei+msg.value;uint256amount=msg.value*tokensPerEth;require(balances[fundsWallet]>=amount);balances[fundsWallet]=balances[fundsWallet].sub(amount);balances[msg.sender]=balances[msg.sender].add(amount);emitTransfer(fundsWallet,msg.sender,amount);fundsWallet.transfer(msg.value);deductToken(amount);}else{revert("Token balance reaches reserve capacity, no more tokens will be given out.");}}
